%U A116096 34182546327286,37487353123861,52213551379230,74230108225630
%N A116096 Numbers k such that k concatenated with k-9 gives the product of two numbers which differ by 4.
%C A116096 If k-9 has d digits, the concatenation is k//k-9 = 10^d*k+k-9 = m*(m+4), therefore k//k-5 = 10^d*k+k-5 = (m+2)^2, so there is a large overlap or equality with A115433. - _R. J. Mathar_, May 22 2026
%e A116096 9900249006//9900248997 = 9949999499 * 9949999503, where // denotes concatenation.
%Y A116096 Cf. A115433, A116095, A116097, A116104, A116227.
